  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="NA389-kiḷavi">
            <p type="edition">itu pakaṟkuṟi vantoḻukāniṉṟa kālattut talaimakaṉ kēṭpac colliyatu.</p>
            <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what was said so that HE would hear in the time [he] kept coming to the day tryst.</p>
            </div>
      <div xml:id="NA389">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            vēṅkai yumpuli yīṉṟaṉa varuviyun</l>
<l>            tēmpaṭu neṭuvarai maṇiyiṉ māṉu</l>
<l>            maṉṉaiyu mamarntunōk kiṉaḷē yeṉṉaiyuṅ</l>
<l>            kaḷiṟṟumukan tiṟanta kallā viḻuttoṭai</l>
<l>            yēva liḷaiyaroṭu māvaḻip paṭṭeṉac </l>
<l>            ciṟukiḷi muraṇiya peruṅkura lēṉal</l>
<l>            kāva liṉiyeṉ ṟōḷē cēvaloṭu</l>
<l>            cilampiṟ pōkiya citarkāl vāraṇa</l>
<l>            mutaiccuvaṟ kiḷaitta pūḻi mikappala</l>
<l>            naṉpo ṉimaikku nāṭaṉō </l>
<l>            ṭaṉpuṟu kāma mamaikanan toṭarpē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>            The Vēṅkai trees have brought forth tigers</l>
<l rend="indent4">            and the waterfalls</l>
<l>        resemble sapphires on the long mountain flowing with honey</l>
<l>        and mother stood still [and] looked [at it].</l>
<l rend="indent4">            And since father</l>
<l rend="indent">            is on the way [to hunt] animals with the youths [he] commands, with</l>
<l rend="indent">             arrows, excellent without teaching, that opened the elephant bull’s face,</l>
<l rend="indent4">            she has said</l>
<l rend="indent2">            “[yours is] the guarding now</l>
<l rend="indent2">            of the big-eared millet on which the small parrots have become many.”</l>
<l>        May our attachment [that is] loving desire be close</l>
<l rend="indent">            with the man from the land, where good gold twinkles,</l>
<l rend="indent2">            very many [bits] in the dust dug up on the old height</l>
<l rend="indent3">            by the hen with spotted legs who had gone to the slope with [her] cock.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
